front.title: •Hutt Bounty
front.gametext: Deploy on an opponent's smuggler, gambler, or thief. If subsequently captured, seized by a bounty hunter and then transfered to Jabba's Palace Dungeon, retrieve Force equal to character's forfeit (+6 if Han) and lose effect. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: 'Chissaa, picha gawanki Chewbacca. Yupon cogorato kama walpa kyess kashung kawa Wookiee.'
